measurements.description:
Approximately 2288 flowers in very fine condition and three buds on 12
highly branched inflorescences approximately 151cm long; exceptionally
well-grown 137x103-cm plant in bark, 36 flat pseudobulbs 13.5x6cm,
 leathery leaves 47x9.2cm, 31-cm bulb pan; sepals and petals
reflexed, coiled, light chartreuse barred light mahogany; lip white, ruffled
side lobes, spotted light brown, claw white spotted light brown, callus
yellow spotted light brown; column chartreuse, column wings white
spotted light brown, anther cap chartreuse; substance soft; texture
matte; all flowers in peak condition influenced the cultural award 20215324 this plant also received.
